This allows you to easily run cheaper, mil-surp 7.61x51 ammo without any concern of light primer strikes.The gun comes with a Lancer L7AWM Smoke Translucent 20 round magazine as pictured, and the Magpul MLOK foregrip and bipod mount are included.This gun shoots great, is really reliable (Especially once you tune the gas system the way you like it) and is extremely accurate. Definitely under 1 MOA if you use match ammo. What you get is a set-up 16” .308 that is ready to go for many applications.
